The paper focuses on designing a natural language interface for dataflow visualization systems, which involves aspects of human-computer interaction (HCI) and natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, cs.HCI and cs.CL are the most likely sub-categories. Additionally, the paper deals with data analysis and visualization, which could fall under cs.DB and cs.IR. Finally, the use of NLP techniques to assist with dataflow diagram construction could also be considered as an application of artificial intelligence (AI), making cs.AI a possible sub-category as well.
